The paper focuses on object detection in the context of robotics and augmented reality, which suggests that it is likely to fall under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The use of deep learning techniques and network architecture also suggests that it could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and graphics (cs.GR) categories.
